    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123140/extras/7d65bfa6f02da43d05f7a6b70d748d98.avif?t=1749388426\" width=616 height=72 /></span>不知从何时起，人类世界的天空被未知的存在撕裂，通向其他次元的裂缝也出现在了世界各处。秽恶的瘴气从这些裂缝中溢出，将本来无害的动物转化成了各种残忍嗜杀的魔物。在人类来到了生死存亡的关头时，一群被神明选中的勇者担下了拯救世界的重责大任，成为了歼魔将。他们发誓要将世界上的邪恶存在赶尽杀绝，并且把邪恶的源头彻底消灭，净化整个世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123140/extras/398fcbd96165b6048ed7cc3c038dc33c.avif?t=1749388426\" width=616 height=72 /></span>艾格尼丝·弗雷亚拜特是其中一只歼魔将家族中最强大的末裔，但她却被王国的宰相设计陷害，失去了所有的力量。在她满足宰相的无理要求前，宰相是绝对不会将原本属于她的力量还给她的。但宰相却没想到，没收歼魔将的力量会加剧世界被邪恶侵蚀的进程。现在艾格尼丝需要找到能让自己的力量恢复的方法，而她的下属也会想方设法为她收集魔力。她究竟能否将邪恶从世界中驱逐，并且粉碎宰相的阴谋呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123140/extras/3aed1a2fbd729999b3a10d3bcc26867e.avif?t=1749388426\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123140/extras/a19684ec5f0297f9bf54d3767bfbf938.avif?t=1749388426\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123140/extras/7f009fff9fc01da1644df94d770194d4.avif?t=1749388426\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123140/extras/bc9fa345fe859160b0e26fe7cfbdd0c5.avif?t=1749388426\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p>",
